  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><strong>Monday 11th April 2016, Godalming</strong>- Inghams’ guests can relax this <a href="/ski-holidays/special-offers/new-year">New Year</a> as they will <strong>arrive in resort on Friday 30th December</strong> ready to enjoy a day on the slopes and find all the local bars before welcoming in 2017. Guests will receive an<strong> 8 night holiday for the price of 7</strong> returning on Saturday 7th January 2017 which includes o<strong>ne night’s free stay worth up to £110 per person. </strong></p>
<p><br />To add to the New Year cheer Inghams is offering an <strong>additional £200 saving</strong> per couple on all chalet and Chalet Hotel New Year bookings made by 31st May 2016.</p>
<p>The offer can be <strong>used in conjunction with any other offer</strong> including enhanced group savings on bookings for over 8 people on peak weeks including New Year made before 18th April 2016.</p>
<p>Why cook and stress this New Year when Inghams has excellent chalet teams across the Alps with a wide variety of choice from small intimate chalets to larger, sociable Chalet Hotels? Furthermore, the Alps is a magical place to spend New Year with fireworks, lavish celebrations, incredible scenery and delicious food!</p>
<p><strong>Sample Packages</strong></p>
<p><br /><strong>New Year in exclusive<a data-udi="umb://document/a0f5a0d90fe3493faa137de4bb419db4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0f5a0d90fe3493faa137de4bb419db4}" title="Verbier"> Verbier</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a>- £1129 per person- saving £380 per couple</strong></p>
<p>Celebrate the New Year in one of Europe’s most stylish and excusive resorts, Verbier- a lively resort with fantastic bars, restaurants and skiing. Inghams is offering 8 nights, chalet catering including a New Year celebration meal with Champagne at the 4.5 diamond<a data-udi="umb://document/eb091d6f78994051880c5f1e85e059bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb091d6f78994051880c5f1e85e059bb}" title="Xtra Chalet de Verbier"> Xtra Chalet Hotel de Verbier,</a> Switzerland from £1129 per person (including £200 saving per couple and a free night’s stay worth £180 per couple) departing Friday 30th December 2016. The holiday avoids New Year’s Eve departures and includes return flights from London Gatwick to Geneva and resort transfers. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk">www.inghams.co.uk</a> or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<p><strong>New Year in <a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a></strong>- <strong>£1259 per person- saving £400 per couple</strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/5e45610b0d27453b8e65a19cbb511b58" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5e45610b0d27453b8e65a19cbb511b58}" title="Chalet Camille">Chalet Camille</a> is a superb chalet in Le Lavachet, Tignes only 30m from the piste and Paquis and Chaudanne ski lifts, the perfect place to welcome in 2017. Inghams is offering 8 nights, chalet catering including a New Year celebration meal with Champagne at the 4 diamond Chalet Camille from £1259 per person (including £200 saving per couple and a free night’s stay worth £200 per couple) departing Friday 30th December 2016. The holiday avoids New Year’s Eve departures and includes return flights from London Gatwick to Geneva and resort transfers. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk%20">www.inghams.co.uk </a>or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<p><strong>New Year in <a data-udi="umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a>,<a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria"> Austria</a></strong>- <strong>£909 per person- saving £340 per couple</strong></p>
<p>The party is in Mayrhofen this New Year which offers extensive nightlife, bars, music and fireworks. Inghams is offering 8 nights, chalet catering including a New Year celebration menu with Champagne at the 3.5 diamond <a data-udi="umb://document/827cb0984fdc4ab4bf4af904cef0da62" href="/{localLink:umb://document/827cb0984fdc4ab4bf4af904cef0da62}" title="Chalet St. Lukas">Chalet St. Lukas</a>, Mayrhofen, Austria from £909 per person (including £200 saving per couple and a free night’s stay worth £140 per couple) departing Friday 30th December 2016. The holiday avoids New Year’s Eve departures and includes return flights from London Gatwick to Innsbruck and resort transfers. For more information or to book visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk">www.inghams.co.uk</a> or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<p><strong>New Year in <a data-udi="umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia</a>,<a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy"> Italy</a>- £1109- saving £380 per couple</strong><br />Chalet Hotel Dragon is in a prime location in Cervinia, 200m from the chairlift, 1 minute from the centre and with its own popular après bar with live music and sun terrace looking out onto the Matterhorn. Inghams is offering 8 nights, chalet catering including a New Year celebration meal with Champagne at the 3.5 diamond Chalet Hotel Dragon, Cervinia, Italy from £1109 per person (including £200 saving per couple and a free night’s stay worth £180 per couple) departing Friday 30th December 2016, price is based on four sharing. The holiday avoids New Year’s Eve departures and includes return flights from London Gatwick to Turin and resort transfers. For more information or to book visit<a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk"> www.inghams.co.uk</a> or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<p>Visit the website or phone our reservations team 01483 791 114 for more information on the full range of <a data-udi="umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257}" title="Chalet">chalet</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/7bfe7675d92e4c888cf5dee0c78eb888" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bfe7675d92e4c888cf5dee0c78eb888}" title="Chalet Hotel">Chalet Hotels</a> or to book.</p>
<p>Offer available on new bookings only for chalet and Chalet Hotels made before 31st May 2016. Terms and conditions apply, subject to availability. <br /><strong>ENDS.</strong></p>
<p><br /><strong>For press enquiries or a copy of the brochure please contact</strong><br />PR Assistant, Rachel Gaston, Inghams on 01483 79 10 45 /<a href="/%20rachel.gaston@inghams.co.uk">rachel.gaston@inghams.co.uk</a><br />Senior PR Account Manager, Daniela Resenterra, 020 7593 1771/<a href="mailto:danielaR@hillsbalfour.com">danielaR@hillsbalfour.com</a><br />Senior PR Account Executive, Josie Self on 020 7593 1758/ <a href="mailto:JosieS@hillsbalfour.com">JosieS@hillsbalfour.com</a></p>]]></bodyText>
